│ [Table embedded]            │
│ Text paragraph (200 words)  │
│ [Chart embedded]            │
└─────────────────────────────┘

BAD - Avoid:
- Full page with only one chart
- Multiple pages of pure text
- Charts grouped at end of sections
""" ;
